<item>
            <title>[LU-2787] review-zfs lustre-initialization_1  It is broken. </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2787</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This is reported in every single patch review. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I didn&apos;t find an LU of this common error so I filed one. It seems very serious.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Perhaps this is a TT issue I don&apos;t know.  I took a quick look at the system logs and all I saw were systems just sitting around for some time.  &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Actual error logs can be seen here:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/216df032-71f8-11e2-aad1-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/216df032-71f8-11e2-aad1-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The tests reports:&lt;br/&gt;
Failure Rate: 44.00% of last 100 executions &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;all branches&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>a patch pushed via git. </environment>
